# 编译中间与产物文件
# ========================
*.obj
*.o
*.i
*.ii
*.s
*.a
*.lib
*.dll
*.exe
*.pdb          # 调试符号文件
*.pch          # 预编译头
*.idb
*.res
*.ilk
*.exp
*.def
*.aps
*.bsc
*.sbr
*.ipdb
*.iobj
*.log
*.tlog

